I found this online with extremely poor quality in the audio, so I synced the CD audio to the video and used that instead. I needed to do some serious time stretching, but it came out great for what it is. For those that don't know, the voice of the teacher is that of one Mrs. Fagan who was actually one of Vai's teachers when he was a kid, in Carle Place! heh Classic! As a kid, I knew I had to learn to jam out as best I could when I first saw this.
